https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NETBEANS-2971

When Within Parentheses - Method / Function Declaration is checked:
```php
$annon = function ($test) use ($lexicalVar) {
    return $test . $lexicalVar;
}
```
before
```php
$annon = function ($test) use ($lexicalVar) {
    return $test . $lexicalVar;
}
```
after
```php
$annon = function ( $test ) use ( $lexicalVar ) {
    return $test . $lexicalVar;
}
```
